- A few link texts and URL paths are inconsistent (e.g., text `docs/archive/mission-geometry.md` but URL `mission-geometry.md`). Prefer text and URL to match.

- `docs/agent-product-doctrine.md` references `docs/definitions/og-dolt-heresy-completion-2026-07-08.md` as plain text rather than a Markdown link at line 8 <ref_snippet file="/Users/wiz/go-choir/docs/agent-product-doctrine.md" lines="6-10" />. Consider making it a link for consistency.

